{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "——第9周的早晨。\n我和菜菜的关系已经完全超越了治疗师和顾客的框架。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(9周...菜菜的身体已经完全绽放。她的心也是...)"
    },
    {
      "include": "common/weekly_settlement"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "早上好...老师...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "早上好,菜菜。今天看起来气色不错。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "那是...可能因为昨晚睡得很好...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "睡得好?那太好了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "是的...最近,身体更容易放松了...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "但是,还是想接受老师的治疗...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "真诚实呢。像这样诚实的菜菜让治疗很有价值。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "老师的治疗...真的很特别...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "那是因为菜菜的身体完美地接受了我的治疗。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_lookaway_openmouth",
      "text": "我的身体已经变成...没有老师的手就无法满足了...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_006"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "(她已经完全依赖我的治疗了...这是完美的状态。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "嗯...今天我有个请求...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_007"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "什么?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_lookaway_openmouth",
      "text": "我想要...更加...激烈的治疗...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_008"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "上次虽然很温柔但是...今天想要更多...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_009"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_lookaway_openmouth",
      "text": "我想要...用力按压...激烈地...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_010"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "激烈?你确定能承受那么强吗?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "最近,温柔的治疗...已经不够了...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_011"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "开始想要...更强的刺激了...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_012"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "这是美妙的变化。这是你诚实面对自己身体的证明。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "都是托老师的福...是你唤醒了我的身体...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_013"
    },
    {
      "id": "choice_massage9",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "我收到你的请求了,菜菜。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "但不要太勉强自己",
          "trustDelta": 2,
          "developDelta": 0,
          "next": "careful_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "今天会用你能承受的最大强度",
          "trustDelta": 1,
          "developDelta": 2,
          "next": "limit_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "你已经完全是我的专属身体了",
          "trustDelta": 0,
          "developDelta": 3,
          "next": "mine_path"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "careful_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_happysmile",
      "text": "是的...老师真温柔。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_014"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "菜菜是重要的客人。作为专业人士,我必须好好照顾你。",
      "next": "prepare_massage"
    },
    {
      "id": "limit_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "能承受的最大强度...?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_015"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "是的。用你所追求的强度,给你前所未有的激烈治疗。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "好、好的...拜托了...",
      "next": "prepare_massage",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_016"
    },
    {
      "id": "mine_path",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "你已经完全是我的专属身体了。没有我的治疗就无法满足,对吧?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "你、你的专属...?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_017"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "这样说...很害羞...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_018"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "但这是事实,不是吗?你的身体现在只对我有反应。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "...可能...是真的...",
      "next": "prepare_massage",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_019"
    },
    {
      "id": "prepare_massage",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "嗯...还有一个请求...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_020"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "什么?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_lookaway_openmouth",
      "text": "今天...那件特殊的衣服...有没有更小的...?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_021"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "再小一点?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "是的...我想露出更多的皮肤...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_022"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_lookaway_openmouth",
      "text": "我想让老师看到一切...触碰一切...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_023"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "(她自己要求更多暴露...已经被完全开发了。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "既然你都这么说了，干脆不穿衣服怎么样?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "诶...?那、那个...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_024"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "还是...太害羞了...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_025"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "开玩笑的。不过既然菜菜这么说了，下次我找找更小的。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "真、真的吗...?谢谢您...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_026"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "那么今天,先穿平时的衣服吧。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_closeeyes_closemouth",
      "text": "(平时的衣服...已经无法满足我了...)",
      "cutInImage": "nana_changing",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_027"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_lookaway",
      "text": "(想要更多...想被看到更多...想被触碰更多...这样的自己...有点...可怕...)",
      "cutInImage": "nana_changing",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_028"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "换、换好了...",
      "outfit": "micro_bikini",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_029"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "(明明应该已经看习惯了...菜菜发育后的身体真是魅力十足...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "老师...今天也请多多关照...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_030"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "完美。菜菜真的很美。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "谢、谢谢...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_031"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "...拜托了...今天想要...特别的治疗...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day9_032"
    },
    {
      "id": "massage_start",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "好的。今天会按照你所期望的深度来治疗你。准备好了吗?"
    }
  ]
}
